OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FShowers
OL,6,Feasing for most, with cloud breaks
OL,7,Fdeveloping. The odd mist or fog
OL,8,Fpatches could then form, and it will
OL,9,Fbe feeling rather cool with light
OL,10,Fwinds. The odd pocket of rural frost
OL,11,Fcannot be completely ruled out.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSaturday:FMostly dry and fine, with
OL,14,Fvariable amounts of cloud and some
OL,15,Fsunny spells. Easterly winds will
OL,16,Fgradually strengthen through the day,
OL,17,Fleading to a cooler feel, especially
OL,18,Falong eastern coasts.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
