OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FFine
OL,6,FSunday, with brighter spells. Cold,
OL,7,Fperhaps frosty start Monday, before
OL,8,Frain band clears south later, followed
OL,9,Fby brighter spells. Clear spells
OL,10,Fovernight, then cloudier Tuesday with
OL,11,Foutbreaks of rain.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
